			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">The Water Is Eating the Island</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">Villagers hang onto the last patch of Sierra Leone’s Nyangai Island, knowing that their home may soon disappear.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
